title: De La Cultura De La Basura

description:
The drum part was almost completely changed, making it similar to the original theme. In the bass part some final parts were changed. The guitar underwent almost no changes, only a missing part was added.
The original tablature lacked the final part of the song, which was eventually added.
The tempo was changed.
